whereas.text:
Whereas the Obama Administration announced on Tuesday
			 March 5, 2013, that it would cancel all White House tours due to
			 sequestration;

Whereas the annual cost to the Secret Service of
			 maintaining the White House open for public tours is approximately $3.7
			 million;

Whereas the President has taken four trips to Hawaii in
			 the past four years, at a cost to the taxpayers of at least $4 million each, as
			 well as numerous other vacations at enormous taxpayer expense;

Whereas the President has the complete discretion to
			 transfer funds in such a way as to keep the White House open for tours;
			 and
